            <div type="transcript" id="F1130C">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Frost of<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Death was on the<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Pane - </l>
                    <l>&quot;Secure your Flower&quot; said he.  </l>
                    <l>Like Sailors<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 fighting with a Leak </l>
                    <l>We fought<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Mortality - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Our passive Flower<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 we held to Sea -<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
</l>
                    <l>To mountain -<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 to the Sun - </l>
                    <l>Yet even on his<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Scarlet shelf </l>
                    <l>To crawl the<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Frost begun - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>We pried him<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 back </l>
                    <l>Ourselves we<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 wedged</l>
                    <l>Himself and her<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 between -<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 </l>
                    <l>Yet easy as the<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 narrow Snake </l>
                    <l>He forked his<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 way along </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Till all her<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 helpless beauty<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 bent </l>
                    <l>And then our<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 wrath begun -</l>
                    <l>We hunted him<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 to his Ravine<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 </l>
                    <l>We chased him<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 to his Den - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>We hated Death<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 and hated Life </l>
                    <l>And nowhere<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 was to go - </l>
                    <l>Than Sea and<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 continent there<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 is</l>
                    <l>A larger - it<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 is Woe </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
